WINDOWS:

copy epimorphism\_lib\source\win\freeglut.dll to C:\WINDOWS\System32
copy epimorphism\_lib\source\win\msvcr32.dll to C:\WINDOWS\System32
install the appropriate PIL package from _lib\source\win\

LINUX:

Dependencies - python2.7, distutils, PIL, freeglut, python-opengl

./epimorphism


OSX:





NEW APP:
 add $app object to config/applications.py
 add config/app/$app_default.app
 add config/state/$app_default.est
 add kernels/$app_kerenls.cl